Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Navio, navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.71,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647.238,290.381)}0 e 4{\fad(900,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,A propósito, você leu O Economista?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,O Economista-reiro, O Economista!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,O jornal O Economista!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Você conhece, certo-reiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A tirinha de O Economista!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, onde aparece um robô gigante dos sonhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Sora, o Guerreiro do Mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu lia muito-reiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sora, um herói que pode andar sobre o mar,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,acompanhado de um robô que\N se transforma em uma gaivota-reiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...lutando contra Germa 66, o exército maligno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.55,Main,,0,0,0,,É a história de um herói da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele tem fãs em todo o mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouvi dizer que Sora, o guerreiro do mar, é baseado nos heróis reais da Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Era para lavar o cérebro das crianças!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Para ensiná-las que a \NMarinha é sempre justa e forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:02.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não era isso que eu gostava!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Era da Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Germa 66!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,O exército maligno que sempre encurralava Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Heróis do mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, eles sempre perdiam por\N conveniência da história,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,mas eu os apoiava com todo o meu ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,A vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me inclua!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho nada a ver com eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Não diga isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em conhecer um pessoalmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, diga a eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, abre!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Porta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,É que...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare de me seguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Este é o meu quarto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Também é o meu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Me tirem daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que me tratam de maneira tão diferente?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um gênio da ciência!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda não desistiu-nyororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Nos ordenaram capturar você e nada mais, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ele é o importante noivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...que unirá a família Vinsmoke\N com a nossa, a família Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Não valem o mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou me casar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Saia daqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Que ele saia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele foi rude com Vito!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:45.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx170\fscy170\bord2.0\pos(640,445)\fad(534,0)}PIRATAS FIRETANK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:45.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx170\fscy170\bord2.0\pos(640,670)\fad(534,0)}GOTTI, "SICÁRIO"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou perdoar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Peça desculpas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotti!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera, espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não me disse muita coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Sem problemas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Era uma brincadeira-reiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotti...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumam daqui, você e Vito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, ele disse de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou perdoar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso, Gotti!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Pode dizer o que quiser para mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não vou perdoar quem insultar meus companheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Não fique assim-reiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá em frente, não me perdoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não quero ser seu amigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotti!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:06:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não sabe que ele é filho dos Vinsmoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ele se machucar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,matarão nosso pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Não entende?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Quer que eu te mate primeiro, cabeça oca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, você...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Dói, dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hoje você não vai comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe o barulho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Conte-me sobre Germa em outro momento...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele se parece muito com ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:12.20,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(537,500)}ALGUNS DIAS DEPOIS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Não aguento mais...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou morrer...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:17.04,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1033.334,455.333)\fscx170\fscy170\bord2.0}No Thousand Sunny{\fad(650,725)} {translated it myself}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Que calor...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou morrer...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(162,775)\bord1.0\fscx140\fscy140\pos(640,530)}(Vou secar...)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(162,775)\bord1.0\fscx140\fscy140\pos(640,530)}(Sanji, comida, sorvete)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Não aguento o calor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Queria tirar esse pelo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós também...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Os minks não aguentam bem o calor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Que calor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou virar uma múmia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma múmia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma múmia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma múmia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, nesse caso,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,é como se ressuscitasse um pouco, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,E eu sei lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, você me mostra sua calcinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho energia para te bater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami, estou com fome e está muito calor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Preciso de nutrientes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Não conseguimos pescar por causa da tempestade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...e agora o céu finalmente clareou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Pesquem antes que o tempo mude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer de fome antes de chegarmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Queríamos fazer isso, mas, Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,O mar está fervendo de tanto calor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Assim, nenhum peixe vai se aproximar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida de emergência...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me olhe assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Fisgou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.26,Main,,0,0,0,,É um peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,É enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Pesque ele, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san, ânimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ânimo, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,É enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele tem uma cor estranha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que é comestível?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos os peixes são comestíveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, espera um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou pesquisar sobre esse peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde está a enciclopédia de peixes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A estante do Sanji está cheia de revistas pornô!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui está!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, esse não é...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui está!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuidado com a pele dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,A pele contém um veneno mortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui está a nota do Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,A pele é deliciosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou assar para você!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Toma, come, Carrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa pele está muito grudenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, nós também...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Está delicioso, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, estou emocionado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou feliz por estar vivo-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Só cozinhei seguindo a receita do Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Chopper, você também precisa de energia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,E-estou com frio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Chorar não vai resolver nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Toma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Você precisa estar saudável para cuidar do Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não tenho plantas medicinais\N suficientes para servir de antídoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos encontrar uma ilha, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos sem ervas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:32.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não dá para encontrar uma ilha tão rápido...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Na enciclopédia de peixes do Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,...diz que você morre imediatamente ao comer a pele, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ele ainda está vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que o Luffy tem bons anticorpos, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele tem uma vitalidade incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ele não está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,O rio é lindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está vendo o rio Sanzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos perto do território da mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:22.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ao redor de Whole Cake Island há várias ilhas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Perna Negra e os outros já devem\N ter passado por essas ilhas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,...e chegado a Whole Cake Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Não baixem a guarda...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou vigiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu planejava desembarcar na primeira ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos conseguir um antídoto lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora está nevando?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Que lindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Essas são nuvens doces?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,E o que está caindo é neve de algodão doce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Algodão doce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Esplêndido, esplêndido!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Doce...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.25,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,300)\fscx170\fscy170\bord2.0\pos(640,705)}Lesma do mar territorial {checked the spanish manga for the translation CH825 P12}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,O Den Den Mushi dele detectou\N as ondas telepáticas de aviso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:47.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que entramos\N no território da Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Algodão doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Escondam-se e disfarcem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Que doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está me ouvindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou vendo algo, Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,É um navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Um navio está vindo nesta direção!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles já estão aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente é um bolo, \Num dos nossos navios de reconhecimento!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,A neblina não me deixa ver bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu cuido disso, vocês se escondam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy está muito pálido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,O veneno continua se espalhando pelo corpo dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,É perigoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos cuidar dele logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Não haverá algum antídoto \Nnesse navio de reconhecimento?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou perguntar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Depressa, escondam-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Chopper-san, depressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Um Den Den Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,É enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem um número escrito nele.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sessenta e seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Germa falando.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Localizamos o navio dos Chapéus de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Um navio do Germa 66?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Germa 66...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,A organização liderada pelo pai do Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo aqui, Piratas do Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos colidir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Gente, amarrem as velas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, espera um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos evitar a colisão...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, essas sobrancelhas em espiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Que alívio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Não esperava vê-lo tão cedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Que sorte...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos um problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy comeu um peixe\N venenoso e está agonizando!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há algum antídoto nesse navio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Parem de dizer Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão enganados!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, é claro que nos parecemos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Meu nome é Yonji!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.49,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,460)\fad(644,0)}GERMA 66
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.49,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(644,0)}VINSMOKE YONJI (WINCH GREEN)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yonji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.33,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Yonji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não é o Sanji, mas o Yonji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo tendo o mesmo rosto \Ne as sobrancelhas em espiral, é outra pessoa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Minha relação com o Sanji, que \Nvocês conhecem, é de máximo segredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.09,Main,,0,0,0,,É completamente confidencial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida de que ele é seu irmão mais novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.76,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida de que ele é seu irmão mais novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Então ele também tinha um irmão mais novo, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você sabe que ele é o irmão mais novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Que linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Linda, linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Você realmente não é o Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yonji-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acho que o Sanji-sama esteja naquele navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que nos desencontramos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos dar meia-volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Perdemos tempo nesta viagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Yonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Os eczemas continuam se espalhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está perdendo resistência!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Que veneno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy tem anticorpos fortes, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, resista!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.40,Main,,0,0,0,,É só o veneno de um peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Você vai ser o Rei dos Piratas, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Não morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês devem ter antídotos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Usamos os nossos, \Nmas ainda não fizeram efeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você é o irmão do Sanji-san, \Npor favor, salve o Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Não estou interessado em salvar pessoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ou vocês vão tentar roubar nosso remédio?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Como fazem os piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,O que há com ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não se parece em nada com o Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo gostando das mesmas garotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não é nada gentil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Se vamos fazer isso, me dê a ordem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare de ser tão egoísta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yonji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Reiju-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:56.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Um invasor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Olá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Meu irmão mais novo é um \Ncriminoso sem um pingo de humanidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Irmão mais novo? {SC785 T2:54}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela é a irmã mais velha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:57.58,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,465)\fad(533,0)}GERMA 66
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:57.58,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(533,0)}VINSMOKE REIJU (POISON PINK)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,As sobrancelhas dela também são em espiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Que linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Reiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está voando?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldita!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você ousa me humilhar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Você deveria se envergonhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela está levitando?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,É ciência!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:23.75,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Germa 66 é um grupo de pessoas que se tornou poderoso graças à ciência.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Pode-se dizer que é um\N esquadrão de lutadores científicos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...nossa mama deseja esse poder!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Pekoms-san, se não me engano, Vinsmoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...é o nome de uma família real, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não me falha a memória,\N é uma família que há muito tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:24:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...conquistou o North Blue com violência!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que é uma família real \Ncomo a de Vivi e Neptune?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa família é tão importante assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, é.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Eram sinônimo do mal em outra época.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.31,0:24:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso os usaram como modelos para uma tira cômica.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhor esqueleto, você sabe muito de história, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vivi muito tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Embora já esteja morto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas isso não é uma história do passado.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.68,0:24:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda somos uma família real.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Germa é um país sem território.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos uma terra para governar, mas podemos participar da Reverie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.41,0:24:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.63,0:24:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, você me permitiria ver suas calcinhas?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:24:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, posso experimentar agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.48,0:25:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que ele comeu um peixe-pedra\N blindado do Mar Ardente, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.48,0:25:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.28,0:25:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.86,0:25:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse veneno tem efeitos característicos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.50,0:25:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Que glutão.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.17,0:25:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Até um gigante morreria imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.24,0:25:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,O que eu faço?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.97,0:25:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, Luffy já não...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.79,0:25:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não estou qualificado para ser médico de bordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.46,0:25:34.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas esse garoto tem sorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.47,0:25:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque, para mim,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.92,0:25:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,esse veneno é um dos meus favoritos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.64,0:25:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,O-O que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.59,0:25:48.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom apetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.03,0:25:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.28,0:25:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.68,0:26:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você sugar o veneno assim, vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.24,0:26:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.08,0:26:05.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Que inveja!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.62,0:26:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Queria estar no seu lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:10.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Embora eu já não tenha...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.84,0:26:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,...lábios!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.40,0:26:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Os eczemas estão se transferindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.27,0:26:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Os eczemas que Luffy tinha desapareceram!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.19,0:27:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Você sugou?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.93,0:27:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.36,0:27:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.31,0:27:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Poison Pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.32,0:27:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.86,0:27:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...Pink?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.84,0:27:28.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigada pela comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:42.84,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê? O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.84,0:27:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.84,0:27:47.52,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.52,0:27:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Que alegria!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.71,0:27:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.64,0:27:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Que alegria!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.98,0:27:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.36,0:27:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu adormeci enquanto comia peixe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.44,0:28:01.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquela pele estava deliciosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.80,0:28:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Sobrou alguma?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.86,0:28:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se lembra?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.49,0:28:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.66,0:28:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma mulher!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.21,0:28:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.29,0:28:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san, ela salvou sua vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.39,0:28:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.70,0:28:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.43,0:28:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.55,0:28:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Então esse é o Chapéu de Palha Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.55,0:28:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.36,0:28:30.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é a irmã mais velha de Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.73,0:28:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:36.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji é parte da família Vinsmoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.94,0:28:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Nosso pai esteve procurando por Sanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.10,0:28:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,que se afastou de nós quando era criança.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.25,0:28:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Há dois anos, quando o pôster de recompensa de Sanji saiu,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.47,0:28:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,nosso pai pediu imediatamente ao Quartel-General da Marinha que o perseguisse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.08,0:28:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas encontraram a \Npessoa errada, um tal de Duval.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.00,0:29:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Duval!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.10,0:29:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1018)}O cara que conhecemos antes de chegar a Sabaody, o dos Tobiuo Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, aquela vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.90,0:29:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san também estava bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.81,0:29:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi recentemente que o Governo nos chamou...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.92,0:29:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,...para nos dizer que finalmente tinham tirado\N uma foto de Perna Negra Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.70,0:29:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...durante o caos causado \Npelo retorno dos Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.95,0:29:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Nosso pai aumentou sua recompensa...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.58,0:29:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...e fez com que mudassem o "dead or alive", vivo ou morto,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.07,0:29:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,para "only alive", apenas vivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.08,0:29:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso o pôster de Sanji sofreu essa modificação.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.38,0:29:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde está Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.74,0:29:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.01,0:29:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Pode estar com Big Mom ou com nosso pai.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.27,0:30:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Viemos buscá-lo, mas parece que nos desencontramos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.07,0:30:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, basta que ele compareça à festa do chá.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.80,0:30:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,E eu também pude ver vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.46,0:30:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por cuidar do meu irmão mais novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Irmã de Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.78,0:30:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por salvar minha vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.88,0:30:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.48,0:30:38.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Me devolva o Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.50,0:30:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é meu companheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.56,0:31:11.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Aconteça o que acontecer, vou resgatá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.52,0:31:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Está vendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.10,0:31:20.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Você salvou nosso inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.06,0:31:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.08,0:31:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é Pekoms, dos Piratas de Big Mom, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.86,0:31:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você está com os Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.45,0:31:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho minhas razões!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.80,0:31:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho nada para conversar com vocês-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.41,0:31:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque ainda não há nenhum vínculo entre nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.00,0:31:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.60,0:31:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer vista grossa por enquanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.58,0:32:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, não queremos causar alvoroço nem provocar o cancelamento do casamento do nosso irmão.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.84,0:32:08.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Será melhor que todos ajam prudentemente.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.36,0:32:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso seria o ideal-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.61,0:32:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Ponha o barco em movimento.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.45,0:32:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Que tenham boa sorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.61,0:32:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que não lutaram contra Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.88,0:32:56.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, não há dúvida de que é o barco deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.88,0:32:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy também está a bordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.54,0:33:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.17,0:33:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
